trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref:System.Type> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en <xref:System.Type>egenskapen (og verdien) av en utskrift maskinvare eller programvare systemkomponent.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty"></xref> class that has the specified property name.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintSystemTypeProperty"> </xref> klasse som ikke har det angitte egenskapsnavnet.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Type> property of a print system object, including casing.
